    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable showroom condition, having been maintained to the most exacting standards of preservation. Every surface, from the hand-finished exterior to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a commitment to excellence. Mechanically flawless and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, this offering represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector who demands nothing short of perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
